===Collected and miscellaneous works in English===
Additional works that have been translated into English are listed below. Most of the works reflect Novalis&#x27;s more philosophical and scientific sides, most of which were not systematically collected, published, and translated until the 20th century. Their publication has called for a reassessment of Novalis and his role as a thinker as well as an artist.
